{"tid":2096882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［黃店告急］深黃美女小食店位於青衣長發商場疑被迫遷 救推","createTime":"2020-07-06T12:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T14:07:14.000Z","uid":315848,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f70d596765cdf7df87415ce614fa2263d6c18b5a","tid":2096882,"uid":315848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:14:06.000Z","msg":"青衣長發商場地下某綠色餐牌既鋪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />久唔久有個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">後生樣靚身材正既姐姐睇鋪</span></strong></span>（冇圖 但去過既人不服來辯） <br />\n昔日既鋪面色彩繽紛 充滿港人心血 如今只能剩下「康復香港 時代抗疫」同埋撕不去的港殤 換上了一張白紙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上面寫住約滿道別 <br />\n雖然食物不是頂級佳餚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢果份支持港人既精神灑滿了鹽酥雞的表面 令鹽酥雞格外美味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見證佢多次既罷工罷市 絕對身體力行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個風扇開咁大 個姐姐仔仲著咁少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩理由唔日日去懲罰佢 合約應該時日無多 連登仔上啊喂！希望大家攞單果時配一句「_ _ _   _ _ 」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a290d41217575f50625485c69a8f989249870304","tid":2096882,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:15:01.000Z","msg":"Hello 無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f17ca6fdae9a65fb445b87f5a9f6086e3499554","tid":2096882,"uid":315848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f70d596765cdf7df87415ce614fa2263d6c18b5a","tid":2096882,"uid":315848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:14:06.000Z","msg":"青衣長發商場地下某綠色餐牌既鋪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />久唔久有個<span style=\"fon